## Read Data

```{r}
library(tidyverse)

df <- read.csv("test_data.csv",
               header = FALSE,
               col.names = c("ts", "cycle", "temp", "press", "co2")) |> 
  mutate(ts_pt = as.POSIXct(ts, origin = "1970-01-01"))


```

```{r}
ggplot(df, aes(ts_pt, co2)) +
  geom_line()
```
